# V2 — Multi-Restaurant Architecture (Company → Branch Hierarchy)

## Problem Statement

V1 is a **single-restaurant** system — all orders, products, expenses go into shared MongoDB collections with no tenant isolation. V2 needs to support:

```
Super Admin → Creates Companies (e.g., "Chicken Delight")
    Company → Creates Branches (individual restaurants)
        Branch → Full restaurant operations (V1 feature set + new roles)
```

