### New Hierarchy

```
Super Admin (Platform Level)
├── Can create/manage Companies
├── Can view all Companies, Branches, Users
├── Platform-wide analytics & settings
│
Company (e.g., "Chicken Delight")
├── Company Admin (Owner)
│   ├── Create/manage Branches
│   ├── Company-wide settings (tax rate, currency, timezone)
│   ├── Company-wide analytics (all branches combined)
│   ├── Manage company-level promos
│   └── Manage company-level menu templates (optional)
│
Branch (e.g., "Chicken Delight - Downtown")
├── Branch Admin
│   ├── Full control of this branch
│   ├── Menu management (products, categories, modifiers)
│   ├── Staff management (assign roles)
│   └── Branch settings
├── Manager
│   ├── Orders dashboard, sales summary, reports
│   ├── Expense management
│   ├── View employees, manage shifts
│   └── Limited settings access
├── Employee / Cashier
│   ├── POS terminal (take orders)
│   ├── Kitchen display
│   └── Reception display
└── Driver
    ├── View assigned deliveries
    ├── Update delivery status
    └── GPS tracking
```

