> [!IMPORTANT]
> ### Key Design Decisions Needing Your Input
>
> 1. **Company Admin vs Branch Admin roles** — Kya Company Admin aur Branch Admin alag login honge ya ek hi admin dono level manage karega?
>
> 2. **Menu sharing between branches** — Kya ek company ke saari branches ka menu same hoga (company-level menu), ya har branch ka apna alag menu hoga?
>
> 3. **Promo codes scope** — Promos company-wide honge ya branch-specific?
>
> 4. **User-frontend (customer ordering)** — Customer ko branch select karna padega ya company select karke phir branch? (e.g., "Chicken Delight → Downtown Branch")
>
> 5. **Super Admin panel** — Abhi super-admin me sirf menu management hai. V2 me super-admin ka kya scope hoga? Sirf company create/manage, ya billing/subscription bhi?

> [!WARNING]
> ### Breaking Changes
> - **Every existing model** gets a new `branchId` + `companyId` field — existing V1 data will need migration
> - **Authentication is mandatory** — No more open API endpoints. Every request needs a JWT token
> - **All API routes change** to include tenant context (e.g., `/api/v2/branches/:branchId/orders`)
> - **Pusher channels** become branch-scoped (e.g., `orders-{branchId}` instead of `orders`)

