## Data Migration Strategy

For existing V1 data to work with V2:

1. Create a default Company: `{ name: "Chicken Delight", slug: "chicken-delight" }`
2. Create a default Branch: `{ companyId: <above>, name: "Main Branch", slug: "main" }`
3. Run migration script to add `companyId` + `branchId` to ALL existing documents
4. Create a default super-admin user
5. Create a default company-admin user

```javascript
// migration script pseudo-code
const defaultCompany = await Company.create({ name: "Chicken Delight", ... });
const defaultBranch = await Branch.create({ companyId: defaultCompany._id, name: "Main Branch", ... });

// Update all existing documents
await Order.updateMany({}, { $set: { companyId: defaultCompany._id, branchId: defaultBranch._id } });
await Product.updateMany({}, { $set: { companyId: defaultCompany._id, branchId: defaultBranch._id } });
// ... repeat for all models
```

